2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses a wireless network using UAVs, which falls under the networking and internet architecture category. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper considers various limited feedback schemes for NOMA transmission, which can be seen as a control problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper focuses on delivering broadband data, which can be considered as a multimedia application. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper involves rigorous derivation and analysis of outage sum rate performance, which can be seen as a computational problem.
